{"tid":2217221,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"Red Velvet Wendy 傷癒後首度拍攝個人畫報！健康模樣無比耀眼","createTime":"2020-09-25T09:32:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-28T14:14:03.000Z","uid":16659,"like":2,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"d276244f25177bfab9db1e4fdbc3736744938ae8","tid":2217221,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T09:32:55.000Z","msg":"不久前和 Red Velvet 成員合體一起帶來翻唱表演的 Wendy，最近更隻身躍上美妝雜誌。期待她接下來的活動！<br />\n<br />\n美妝雜誌《BEAUTY+》今天（25 日）公開與 Wendy 攜手拍攝的新畫報，乾淨典雅的妝容搭上散發早秋氣息的服飾，更襯托出 Wendy 溫和的知性氣息。<br />\n<br />\n去年底 Wendy 因參加音樂頒獎典禮表演時受傷，不得不投入長達八個月的治療和休養，直到 8 月中時才和成員們一起翻唱經典歌曲 &ldquo;Milky Way&rdquo; 慶祝大前輩 BoA 出道廿年，開心唱歌的模樣讓許多粉絲感動不已。<br />\n<br />\nWendy 的新畫報收錄在《BEAUTY+》10 月號中，有興趣的 ReVeluv 不妨收藏一本囉！"},{"pid":"8adb6bac7c8310da85bc94f9a0ea537cff6c6774","tid":2217221,"uid":16659,"like":1,"dislike":9,"score":-8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T09:33:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/800_86400_b0aabfe7bb9712e6ddabfe74a6112c5e/static.koreastardaily.com/2020-09-25/130375-876200.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F800_86400_b0aabfe7bb9712e6ddabfe74a6112c5e%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2020-09-25%2F130375-876200.png&h=69c38778&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_536410dc20e0d9dcbd85dc701a3cefba/static.koreastardaily.com/2020-09-25/130375-876203.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_536410dc20e0d9dcbd85dc701a3cefba%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2020-09-25%2F130375-876203.jpg&h=3141c176&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_262189b24768c32e878e2ef8885aba69/static.koreastardaily.com/2020-09-25/130375-876205.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_262189b24768c32e878e2ef8885aba69%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2020-09-25%2F130375-876205.jpg&h=7de95924&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"cd0753274e3fc236292bd4b9f419